description: Deletes specified tags from an Batch resource.

parameters.name: resourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource from which to delete tags. Batch resources that support tags are compute environments, jobs, job definitions, job queues, and scheduling policies. ARNs for child jobs of array and multi-node parallel (MNP) jobs aren't supported.

parameters.name: tagKeys
parameters.description: The keys of the tags to be removed. (string) ---
